### Login como Professor
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomeUsuario": "professor1",
  "senha": "senha123"
}

### Login como Aluno
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomeUsuario": "aluno1",
  "senha": "senha123"
}

### Login com credenciais inválidas
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nomeUsuario": "usuario_inexistente",
  "senha": "senha_errada"
}

### Logout (requer token válido)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer [INSERIR TOKEN AQUI (sem as aspas)]


### Criar Turma (Professor)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/turmas
Authorization: Bearer [TOKEN_PROFESSOR]
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "disciplina_id": 1,
  "horario": "21"
}

### Listar Turmas
GET http://localhost:5001/api/turmas
Authorization: Bearer [TOKEN_ALUNO_OU_PROFESSOR]

### Matricular em Turma (Aluno)
POST http://localhost:5001/api/matriculas
Authorization: Bearer [TOKEN_ALUNO]
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "turma_id": 1
}